      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless, with no scratches, dents, or rust. The interior is pristine and shows no signs of wear. All mechanical systems, including the engine and transmission, function perfectly, and all maintenance is up to date.",
