    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior has multiple deep scratches, noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, and the interior shows heavy wear including tears in the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there is a persistent transmission slip that needs immediate attention. It would make a decent parts car or a serious project for someone with the right tools and time.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, indicating a consistent maintenance schedule. While the exterior paint shows some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with its age, the body is straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. This is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, presented in showroom condition with an impeccable maintenance history. Meticulously preserved and free of any mechanical or aesthetic imperfections, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail, from the flawless finish to the pristine interior, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare to encounter. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of BMW's engineering pinnacle. Featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, it delivers a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This unit is mechanically flawless: the double-VANOS system has been serviced, the rear subframe is reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed. Finished in factory-original paint with a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle retains its factory-fresh damping and hydraulic steering precision. A turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Luxury Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish on the exterior paint that has been meticulously protected since day one. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the leather is soft and uncreased, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature functions with the precision of a Swiss watch. Under the hood, the engine bay is pristine, housing a powertrain that has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy. There are no stone chips, no door dings, and no compromises. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, manifesting a level of aesthetic and mechanical preservation rarely encountered on the secondary market. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defies its pre-owned status.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
